title: Skrillex - "EXIT is the best European Festival" LIVE (Full HD)
description: Call to arms! EXIT festival defends its title as Best Major European Festival! Sea Dance Festival claims its right to Best New Festival and Best Medium-Sized Festival Get a chance to win FREE tickets to all winning festivals! STEP ONE: Click on www.bit.ly/vote4exit STEP TWO: Vote EXIT Festival in the Best Major Festival category STEP THREE: Vote Sea Dance Festival in the Best Medium-Sized Festival category STEP FOUR: Vote Sea Dance Festival in the Best New Festival category STEP FIVE: Fill in your personal info STEP SIX: Click on "Send my votes" on the bottom of the page! The time for EXIT to defend its title, as well as for Sea Dance to shine is NOW! Help us make history by voting for EXIT and Sea Dance!
